# Executive Summary

A brute force attack targeting Remote Desktop Protocol (RDP) authentication was detected against a Windows system within the SOC lab environment.

The attack generated a high volume of failed login attempts against the account `bfish` using Hydra v9.5 and was successfully identified through Windows Security Event ID 4625 monitoring in the Elastic Stack SIEM platform.

